{"tid":1357313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同我全部翻翻主線任務!","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:53:00.000Z","uid":201268,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8444921e510dd0306646c14ef2c4db9481ce814f","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"我係到同大家講 全撚部同我推翻<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721</span></span>啲POST上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知元朗件事令大家又憤怒又恐懼 但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721</span></span>先係我地最主線任務!<br />\n我地要對準返個五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n官警黑勾結已經唔係第一日既事 元朗既事係令政府既黑暗面浮左上面 亦提醒左好多人需要自組<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">保衛隊</span></span>及需要自我提升訓練黎保護自己 係<span style=\"color: red;\">男女</span>都要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人只能自己救自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隨時都要提高警覺<br />\n唔理依家係咪黑食黑<br />\n<br />\n依家只有依再大訴求先救到香港同救到元朗班居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劍應指向政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有721既手足既宣言<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=5a7378fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我通通推翻721POST上去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><code>要一網打盡就只能改朝換姓</code></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><code>寧為玉碎 不為瓦全</code></span>"},{"pid":"321a155b4679319ebb126a5fd1c0c90eaef12703","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d7a8e2e985d3a8ad5304646d4cdaececd19eb3","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4c41dc176569b6d5167de9416e19c32ce4781c","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e169fa7477745f50ae6edef924c1acc43dba03","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea529c4fd9ba2d36ae6bf3b3827524e9ae39cd33","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ebb25a6d531ebc16d4a923e99bddabdae52322","tid":1357313,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dde62efca