style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我通通推翻721POST上去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><code>要一網打盡就只能改朝換姓</code></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><code>寧為玉碎 不為瓦全</code></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"其實元朗可以歸入第四個訴求：<br />\n徹底追究警隊濫權情況"},{"pid":"879901c522a64565379956d202144e4131c0749b","tid":1357313,"uid":78414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:52:33.000Z","msg":"請大家推上環義士情況，元朗鄉黑文宣post<br />\n中共用鄉黑警搞恐怖襲擊、<br />\n上環黑警開槍諗住殺義士<br />\n文宣要做足<br />\n重申五大訴求<br />\n連儂牆、傳單，放映會<br />\n宣傳727，召集民防隊"},{"pid":"cdc2bf79806b0fa3be21ebe188356ea4ac566467","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba554f5eddc3b608c1d75ba3693d5f507012f278","tid":1357313,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8444921e510dd0306646c14ef2c4db9481ce814f","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"我係到同大家講 全撚部同我推翻<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721</span></span>啲POST上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知元朗件事令大家又憤怒又恐懼 但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721</span></span>先係我地最主線任務!<br />\n我地要對準返個五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n官警黑勾結已經唔係第一日既事 元朗既事係令政府既黑暗面浮左上面 亦提醒左好多人需要自組<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">保衛隊</span></span>及需要自我提升訓練黎保護自己 係<span style=\"color: red;\">男女</span>都要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人只能自己救自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隨時都要提高警覺<br />\n唔理依家係咪黑食黑<br />\n<br />\n依家只有依再大訴求先救到香港同救到元朗班居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劍應指向政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有721既手足既宣言<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=5a7378fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我通通推翻721POST上去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><code>要一網打盡就只能改朝換姓</code></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><code>寧為玉碎 不為瓦全</code></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"其實元朗可以歸入第四個訴求：<br />\n徹底追究警隊濫權情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"係 所以五大訴求係超級重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04f12febdc9eb1e62ecb3a91b5d5cf305716d3e","tid":1357313,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"元朗唔係主線咩?"},{"pid":"b6149555e94daf26e53b40bdaddbb5824b29132b","tid":1357313,"uid":78250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"推 721 上環post"},{"pid":"07be7952f0d6645c829dcdf1159be8dba99b5372","tid":1357313,"uid":126535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2c1094e0c778d103112c3532cd826fd75630c5","tid":1357313,"uid":201268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPtPn1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPtPn1H.jpg&h=04dbaae4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5c9a1aa6a1e5f49edba1ac463d85b245961a2e1","tid":1357313,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,